#: ../../24.04/index.md:730 be81412ec64d49d08922d162e6026fc3
msgid "More"
msgstr ""

#: ../../24.04/index.md:731 39fd9908f1d14de89997e4f4d9e85ea3
msgid ""
"Support for zero-copy-send on Linux, which reduces CPU usage on the "
